(on it. My fingers were moving but I wasn?t really thinking. So I needed a reliable way to) Tj
T*
(interrupt my ?unproductive productivity? and actually think. The obvious solution was a timer.) Tj
T*
(Unfortunately, if you use timers a lot, you learn to dismiss them reflexively. And it?s really) Tj
